# fetchResultBeforeChanges

**Instance Property**

The original fetch result, without recent changes.

## Declaration

```swift
var fetchResultBeforeChanges: PHFetchResult<ObjectType> { get }
```

## Discussion

This property’s value is the same object you passed to the [doc://com.apple.photokit/documentation/Photos/PHChange/changeDetails(for:)-33a6n] method to request change details.

## Getting the Changed Fetch Result

- **fetchResultAfterChanges**: The current fetch result, incorporating recent changes.
